Business Brief -- Claire's Stores Inc.:
   Sale Is Planned of Division
   To Baraka Art  Frame
Rowland Schaefer, Claire's Stores chairman and president,
said in a statement, "This restructuring not only increases
future earnings estimates by removing the dilutive effect of
continued losses at Decor, but more importantly, it allows
management to concentrate its efforts on our fashion
accessory business, which has historically produced superior
returns."